msgid "Checkbox Background"
msgstr "Kontrollkästchen-Hintergrund"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1247
msgid "Checkmark Color"
msgstr "Häkchenfarbe"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1256
msgid "Border Style"
msgstr "Rahmenstil"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1267
msgid "Border Width (px)"
msgstr "Rahmenbreite (px)"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1272
msgid "Checkbox Border Radius (px)"
msgstr "Kontrollkästchen-Eckenradius (px)"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1286
msgid "Spinner Background Color"
msgstr "Ladekreis-Hintergrundfarbe"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1290
msgid "Spinner Color"
msgstr "Ladekreisfarbe"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1374 includes/class-cap-settings.php:1453
#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1828
msgid "Unauthorized."
msgstr "Nicht autorisiert."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1498
msgid "No instance URL configured."
msgstr "Keine Instanz-URL konfiguriert."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1505
msgid "No Site Key configured."
msgstr "Kein Website-Schlüssel konfiguriert."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1512
msgid "Secret Key is empty."
msgstr "Geheimschlüssel ist leer."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1561
msgid ""
"Forbidden (HTTP 403). The request was blocked. This can occur if \"Block Non-"
"Browser User Agents\" is enabled on your Cap server, as connection checks "
"from the WordPress backend do not use a browser User-Agent."
msgstr ""
"Verboten (HTTP 403). Die Anfrage wurde blockiert. Dies kann auftreten, wenn "
"\"Block Non-Browser User Agents\" auf Ihrem Cap-Server aktiviert ist, da "
"Verbindungsprüfungen vom WordPress-Backend keinen Browser-User-Agent "
"verwenden."

#. translators: 1: HTTP status code
#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1567
#, php-format
msgid "Server responded with HTTP %d — check your endpoint URL and Site Key."
msgstr ""
"Server antwortete mit HTTP %d — überprüfen Sie Ihre Endpunkt-URL und den "
"Website-Schlüssel."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1583
msgid ""
"Unauthorized origin. The Cap server has restricted access to other domains."
msgstr ""
"Nicht autorisierter Ursprung. Der Cap-Server hat den Zugriff auf andere "
"Domains beschränkt."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1605
msgid "Failed to contact siteverify endpoint."
msgstr "Fehler beim Kontaktieren des siteverify-Endpunkts."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1617
msgid ""
"✓ Connection successful — Cap server is reachable and responding correctly."
msgstr ""
"✓ Verbindung erfolgreich — Cap-Server ist erreichbar und antwortet korrekt."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1622
msgid "Siteverify endpoint not found (HTTP 404). Check your instance URL."
msgstr ""
"Siteverify-Endpunkt nicht gefunden (HTTP 404). Überprüfen Sie Ihre Instanz-"
"URL."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1627
msgid "Invalid Site Key or Secret Key."
msgstr "Ungültiger Website-Schlüssel oder Geheimschlüssel."

#. translators: 1: HTTP status code
#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1643
#, php-format
msgid "Siteverify responded with HTTP %d."
msgstr "Siteverify antwortete mit HTTP %d."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1745
msgid "CapConnect security warning:"
msgstr "CapConnect-Sicherheitswarnung:"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1746
msgid ""
"The login captcha is disabled by TPOW_DISABLE_LOGIN_CAPTCHA. Remove the "
"constant from wp-config.php immediately after access has been restored."
msgstr ""
"Das Login-Captcha ist durch TPOW_DISABLE_LOGIN_CAPTCHA deaktiviert. "
"Entfernen Sie die Konstante unmittelbar nach der Wiederherstellung des "
"Zugriffs aus der wp-config.php."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1769
msgid "CapConnect for WP:"
msgstr "CapConnect für WP:"

#. translators: 1: settings link HTML
#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1773
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Please configure the Instance URL, Site Key, and Secret Key in the %1$s to "
"enable captcha protection."
msgstr ""
"Bitte konfigurieren Sie die Instanz-URL, den Website-Schlüssel und den "
"Geheimschlüssel in den %1$s, um den Captcha-Schutz zu aktivieren."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1774 includes/class-cap-settings.php:1815
msgid "settings"
msgstr "Einstellungen"

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1809
msgid "CapConnect Alert:"
msgstr "CapConnect-Warnung:"

#. translators: 1: error message, 2: settings link HTML
#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1813
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Connection to the Cap server is failing. Error: %1$s. Please check your %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Die Verbindung zum Cap-Server schlägt fehl. Fehler: %1$s. Bitte überprüfen "
"Sie Ihre %2$s."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1857
msgid "Empty error message."
msgstr "Leere Fehlermeldung."

#: includes/class-cap-settings.php:1862
msgid ""
"Customize the text labels shown on the widget. Leave them empty to use the "
"localized defaults based on WordPress language settings."
msgstr ""
"Passen Sie die auf dem Widget angezeigten Textbeschriftungen an. Lassen Sie "
"sie leer, um die lokalisierten Standardwerte basierend auf den WordPress-"
"Spracheinstellungen zu verwenden."

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:72
msgid ""
"Captcha recovery is active for one administrator account. Enter that "
"account’s username and password to continue."
msgstr ""
"Die Captcha-Wiederherstellung ist für ein Administratorkonto aktiv. Geben "
"Sie den Benutzernamen und das Passwort dieses Kontos ein, um fortzufahren."

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:83
msgid "Captcha failed? Try administrator recovery."
msgstr "Captcha fehlgeschlagen? Versuchen Sie es mit der Wiederherstellung."

#. translators: %s: Website name.
#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:225
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] Administrator captcha recovery"
msgstr "[%s] Administrator-Captcha-Wiederherstellung"

#. translators: 1: Website name, 2: Recovery URL.
#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:230
#, php-format
msgid ""
"A captcha recovery was requested for an administrator account on %1$s.\n"
"\n"
"Confirm the request using this link:\n"
"%2$s\n"
"\n"
"The link expires in 15 minutes. It does not log anyone in; the correct "
"username and password are still required. If you did not request this email, "
"you can ignore it."
msgstr ""
"Für ein Administratorkonto auf %1$s wurde eine Captcha-Wiederherstellung "
"angefordert.\n"
"\n"
"Bestätigen Sie die Anfrage über diesen Link:\n"
"%2$s\n"
"\n"
"Der Link läuft nach 15 Minuten ab. Er meldet niemanden an; der korrekte "
"Benutzername und das korrekte Passwort sind weiterhin erforderlich. Wenn Sie "
"diese E-Mail nicht angefordert haben, können Sie sie ignorieren."

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:354
#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:409
msgid "Captcha Recovery"
msgstr "Captcha-Wiederherstellung"

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:357
msgid ""
"If an eligible administrator account matches the information provided, a "
"recovery email has been sent."
msgstr ""
"Wenn die Angaben zu einem berechtigten Administratorkonto passen, wurde eine "
"Wiederherstellungs-E-Mail gesendet."

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:360
#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:377
#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:399
#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:417
msgid "Back to login"
msgstr "Zurück zur Anmeldung"

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:368
msgid "Administrator username or email address"
msgstr "Administrator-Benutzername oder E-Mail-Adresse"

#: includes/class-cap-login-recovery.php:371
msgid ""
"We will send a short-lived captcha recovery link to the email address stored "
"on the administrator account."
msgstr ""
